    {
      "start": 494.52,
      "end": 496.02,
      "text": "come to the wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 496.02,
      "end": 496.96,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 496.96,
      "end": 497.56,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 497.56,
      "end": 498.38,
      "text": "그동안에"
    },
    {
      "start": 498.38,
      "end": 499.6,
      "text": "But in the meantime"
    },
    {
      "start": 499.6,
      "end": 500.78,
      "text": "대체한다면"
    },
    {
      "start": 500.78,
      "end": 501.36,
      "text": "meanwhile"
    },
    {
      "start": 501.36,
      "end": 502.92,
      "text": "이렇게 대체할 수도 있겠죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 502.92,
      "end": 504.28,
      "text": "Come to the wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 504.28,
      "end": 505.42,
      "text": "결혼식에"
    },
    {
      "start": 505.42,
      "end": 506.6,
      "text": "참석해 주세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 506.6,
      "end": 507.6,
      "text": "라는 표현입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 507.6,
      "end": 509.0,
      "text": "We can get to know"
    },
    {
      "start": 509.0,
      "end": 510.28,
      "text": "each other better"
    },
    {
      "start": 510.28,
      "end": 512.08,
      "text": "Do they need to know"
    },
    {
      "start": 512.08,
      "end": 512.82,
      "text": "each other better?"
    },
    {
      "start": 513.04,
      "end": 514.0,
      "text": "I don't think so"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.0,
      "end": 515.72,
      "text": "They're business partners"
    },
    {
      "start": 515.72,
      "end": 517.42,
      "text": "potential business partners"
    },
    {
      "start": 517.42,
      "end": 519.36,
      "text": "지금 경영장부라든지"
    },
    {
      "start": 519.36,
      "end": 520.26,
      "text": "아니면 인도의"
    },
    {
      "start": 520.26,
      "end": 521.64,
      "text": "아동 실태에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 521.64,
      "end": 522.66,
      "text": "좀 객관적인"
    },
    {
      "start": 522.66,
      "end": 524.26,
      "text": "리포트를"
    },
    {
      "start": 524.26,
      "end": 525.3,
      "text": "더 잘"
    },
    {
      "start": 525.3,
      "end": 526.54,
      "text": "보고를 받아야 되는"
    },
    {
      "start": 526.54,
      "end": 527.28,
      "text": "상황일 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 527.28,
      "end": 528.94,
      "text": "서로에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 528.94,
      "end": 530.72,
      "text": "더 잘 알아야 된다는"
    },
    {
      "start": 530.72,
      "end": 531.24,
      "text": "이야기네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 531.24,
      "end": 531.8,
      "text": "Personally"
    },
    {
      "start": 531.8,
      "end": 532.24,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 532.24,
      "end": 533.44,
      "text": "They can do business"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.44,
      "end": 534.46,
      "text": "over a cup of coffee"
    },
    {
      "start": 534.46,
      "end": 535.58,
      "text": "in the office"
    },
    {
      "start": 535.58,
      "end": 536.56,
      "text": "at a restaurant"
    },
    {
      "start": 536.56,
      "end": 537.68,
      "text": "It's easy, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 538.14,
      "end": 539.38,
      "text": "But what can they do"
    },
    {
      "start": 539.38,
      "end": 540.68,
      "text": "at her daughter's wedding?"
    },
    {
      "start": 541.38,
      "end": 542.3,
      "text": "What can they do there?"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.68,
      "end": 543.52,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 543.52,
      "end": 544.66,
      "text": "자 계속해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 544.66,
      "end": 545.94,
      "text": "이자벨이 뭐라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 545.94,
      "end": 546.82,
      "text": "대답을 하는지"
    },
    {
      "start": 546.82,
      "end": 547.48,
      "text": "들어보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.48,
      "end": 549.78,
      "text": "I have a flight to India?"
    },
    {
      "start": 550.1,
      "end": 551.32,
      "text": "당연한 반응이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 551.32,
      "end": 552.78,
      "text": "I have a flight to India"
    },
    {
      "start": 552.78,
      "end": 555.24,
      "text": "저는 인도로 가는"
    },
    {
      "start": 555.24,
      "end": 556.44,
      "text": "비행기를 타야 해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 556.44,
      "end": 557.68,
      "text": "라는 의미가 되겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 557.68,
      "end": 559.52,
      "text": "She really wants to get on that flight"
    },
    {
      "start": 559.52,
      "end": 560.48,
      "text": "ASAP"
    },
    {
      "start": 560.48,
      "end": 562.76,
      "text": "She also had a special plan"
    },
    {
      "start": 562.76,
      "end": 564.66,
      "text": "for a little child"
    },
    {
      "start": 564.66,
      "end": 565.26,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 565.32,
      "end": 566.84,
      "text": "Yeah, the kid that she has raised"
    },
    {
      "start": 566.84,
      "end": 568.56,
      "text": "since he was one years old"
    },
    {
      "start": 568.56,
      "end": 570.12,
      "text": "The little cute boy"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.12,
      "end": 571.38,
      "text": "who is so cute in this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 571.38,
      "end": 572.8,
      "text": "아주 아주 귀여운 인도"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.8,
      "end": 574.66,
      "text": "꼬마 소년이 있었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 574.66,
      "end": 576.82,
      "text": "그 아이의 birthday가 있었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.82,
      "end": 578.42,
      "text": "그래서 그 날에 맞춰서"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.42,
      "end": 580.44,
      "text": "꼭 인도로 돌아가려고 했죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 580.44,
      "end": 581.9,
      "text": "Well, you know"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.9,
      "end": 583.24,
      "text": "Staying the weekend"
    },
    {
      "start": 583.24,
      "end": 584.62,
      "text": "won't kill you"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.62,
      "end": 586.52,
      "text": "아주 쉽게 이야기하네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 586.52,
      "end": 587.78,
      "text": "Well, you know"
    },
    {
      "start": 587.78,
      "end": 588.76,
      "text": "Staying the weekend"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.76,
      "end": 589.76,
      "text": "won't kill you"
    },
    {
      "start": 589.76,
      "end": 591.14,
      "text": "해석되시죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.5,
      "end": 592.9,
      "text": "Staying the weekend"
    },
    {
      "start": 592.9,
      "end": 594.72,
      "text": "won't kill you"
    },
    {
      "start": 594.72,
      "end": 597.17,
      "text": "똑같이 표현하지 않나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.37,
      "end": 597.89,
      "text": "우리말로도"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.89,
      "end": 598.39,
      "text": "In Korean?"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.55,
      "end": 599.61,
      "text": "How do you say it in Korean?"
    },
    {
      "start": 599.61,
      "end": 600.53,
      "text": "그러니까 뭐"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.53,
      "end": 603.33,
      "text": "주말 동안 머문다고 해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 603.33,
      "end": 605.25,
      "text": "그게 너를 어떻게 잡아먹지 않아"
    },
    {
      "start": 605.25,
      "end": 606.03,
      "text": "이런 말 있잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.03,
      "end": 607.79,
      "text": "It's fine"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.79,
      "end": 609.79,
      "text": "무슨 큰일이 나는 건 아니잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.79,
      "end": 611.07,
      "text": "라는 의미가 되겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.07,
      "end": 612.17,
      "text": "No problem"
    },
    {
      "start": 612.17,
      "end": 613.01,
      "text": "Relax"
    },
    {
      "start": 613.01,
      "end": 614.37,
      "text": "그러니까 지금"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.37,
      "end": 615.67,
      "text": "테레사는 계속해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.67,
      "end": 617.03,
      "text": "Just kept trying to hold"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.03,
      "end": 617.95,
      "text": "이자벨"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.95,
      "end": 618.37,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.75,
      "end": 620.23,
      "text": "Yeah, don't go"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.23,
      "end": 621.33,
      "text": "Whatever you do"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.33,
      "end": 623.07,
      "text": "You need to stay in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.07,
      "end": 625.05,
      "text": "She's not comfortable in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.05,
      "end": 628.07,
      "text": "She's lived in India so long"
    },
    {
      "start": 628.07,
      "end": 631.01,
      "text": "That New York is like a foreign place to her"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.01,
      "end": 632.89,
      "text": "Even though she used to live there"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.89,
      "end": 634.17,
      "text": "Way back when"
    },
    {
      "start": 634.17,
      "end": 636.43,
      "text": "너무 오랫동안 인도에 머물다 보니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.43,
      "end": 638.01,
      "text": "문화적인 괴리감도 되려"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.01,
      "end": 639.25,
      "text": "느끼고 있는 것 같았어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.25,
      "end": 640.61,
      "text": "아무튼 이 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.61,
      "end": 641.55,
      "text": "한 번 더 들어보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.55,
      "end": 643.57,
      "text": "I just have"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.57,
      "end": 645.75,
      "text": "I have a big weekend ahead of me"
    },
    {
      "start": 645.75,
      "end": 647.35,
      "text": "So why don't you leave all this with me"
    },
    {
      "start": 647.35,
      "end": 648.39,
      "text": "And we'll have lunch on Monday"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.39,
      "end": 649.37,
      "text": "And I'll tell you what I can do"
    },
    {
      "start": 649.37,
      "end": 650.57,
      "text": "But in the meantime"
    },
    {
      "start": 650.57,
      "end": 651.77,
      "text": "Come to the wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 651.77,
      "end": 652.97,
      "text": "We can get to know each other better"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.97,
      "end": 654.09,
      "text": "I have a flight to India"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.09,
      "end": 654.87,
      "text": "Well, you know"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.87,
      "end": 656.98,
      "text": "Staying the weekend won't kill you"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.98,
      "end": 659.0,
      "text": "조미선님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.0,
      "end": 660.54,
      "text": "예습하고 들었더니"
    },
    {
      "start": 660.54,
      "end": 662.12,
      "text": "확실히 잘 들리네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 662.12,
      "end": 664.04,
      "text": "내일도 예습하고 와야겠네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 664.04,
      "end": 664.48,
      "text": "흐흐"
    },
    {
      "start": 664.48,
      "end": 665.36,
      "text": "하셨습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 665.36,
      "end": 666.2,
      "text": "Yes, 예습"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.2,
      "end": 667.7,
      "text": "The power of 예습"
    },
    {
      "start": 667.7,
      "end": 668.46,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 668.46,
      "end": 669.5,
      "text": "아, 들으셨죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.5,
      "end": 671.2,
      "text": "예습에는 파워가 있습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 671.2,
      "end": 672.5,
      "text": "강추합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 672.5,
      "end": 674.1,
      "text": "네, 오늘 스크린 잉글리쉬는"
    },
    {
      "start": 674.1,
      "end": 675.26,
      "text": "여기서 마무리하겠습니다"
    }
  ]
}